# Common Pitfalls

## Forgetting to Handle All Cases

```lean
-- Error: missing cases
example (n : Nat) (h : n < 3) : n = 0 ∨ n = 1 ∨ n = 2 := by
  rcases n with _ | n'
  · left; rfl
  -- Need to handle the successor case!
  · omega
```
